# {{ plugin_name }}

> {{ description }}

An [OpenClaw](https://github.com/openclaw) **Memory** plugin scaffolded with [ClawForge](https://github.com/hidearmoon/clawforge).

## Supported Actions

| Action | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `store` | Persist a memory item |
| `recall` | Query stored memories |
| `delete` | Remove a memory item |
| `clear` | Wipe all memories for a session |

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Development

```bash
clawforge dev .   # hot-reload sandbox
pytest            # run tests
```

